'''''Blues for Smoke''''' is an album by pianist [[Jaki Byard]] recorded in 1960 and released on the [[Candid Records|Candid]] label.<ref>[http://www.bsnpubs.com/cadence/candid.html Candid Records discography] accessed July 30, 2012</ref> 

==Reception==
{{Album ratings
| rev1 = [[Allmusic]]
| rev1Score = {{rating|4.5|5}}<ref name="Allmusic"/> 
}}
[[Allmusic]] awarded the album 4<U+00BD> stars with its review by Scott Yanow stating, "A highly recommended outing from a very underrated pianist".<ref name="Allmusic">Yanow, S. [http://www.allmusic.com/album/blues-for-smoke-mw0000091532 Allmusic Review], accessed July 27, 2012</ref>

== Track listing ==
''All compositions by Jaki Byard''
