# "Aluminum Baby" - 4:32     
# "Pete and Thomas (Tribute to the Ticklers)" - 3:41     
# "Spanish Tinge No 1" - 4:12     
# "Flight of the Fly" - 5:44     
# "Blues for Smoke" - 4:52     
# "Jaki's Blues Next" - 2:07     
# "Diane's Melody" - 5:05     
# "One Two Five" - 2:40  

